Package net.marfgamer.jraknet.client.discovery

Class DiscoveredServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.marfgamer.jraknet.client.discovery.DiscoveredServer

  • public class DiscoveredServer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a server that has been discovered by the RakNetClient and also stores the discovered server's address and Identifier which are both crucial to making use of this class.
    Author:
    Whirvis "MarfGamer" Ardenaur
